reviewText: This was very good it was an older movie but I enjoyed it so much it was adventurous mysterious and magical

I grew up watching this gem. I originally owned it on VHS. But when it was released on DVD, the price was way too steep. Making it hard to buy.

When I saw this had been re-released a couple of weeks ago, I was so over the moon and quickly got a copy. This excellent show was a hit years ago and will always remain one in my view.

The DVD features an interview with Siri Neal grown up.
